## Structure

Only document what's non-obvious. Skip standard conventions.

```
[e.g.]
app/services/     ← all business logic, always use service objects
app/clients/      ← all external API calls, nowhere else
app/queries/      ← complex ActiveRecord queries
app/jobs/         ← background jobs, must be idempotent
spec/             ← mirrors app/ structure
```

