## Git flow

- Branches: `feat/`, `fix/`, `chore/`, `refactor/`, `docs/`
- Commits: Conventional Commits (`feat:`, `fix:`, `chore:`, etc.)
- PRs: small and single-purpose, one concern per PR
- Never push directly to `main`

